Package: saeonobsr
Type: Package
Title: Query and Download Data from the South African Environmental Observation Network (SAEON) Observations Database
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2022-04-26
Author: Glenn Moncrieff <glenn@saeon.ac.za>
Maintainer: Glenn Moncrieff <glenn@saeon.ac.za>
Description: Provides functions to query available datasets and download selected datasets from the SAEON observations database. Additional functionality allows spatial queries and combining of similar observations from separate datasets.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15)
Imports:
    sf,
    httr,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    lubridate,
    purrr,
    magrittr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
URL: https://github.com/GMoncrieff/saeonobsr
BugReports: https://github.com/GMoncrieff/saeonobsr/issues
